dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jerry Wilson. May I have your name, please?
Hi Jerry, my name is Cheryl Peterson.
Nice to meet you, Cheryl. Before we proceed, could you kindly provide me with your policy number?
Sure, my policy number is zero zero two four six.
Great, thank you. One last thing, Cheryl. Can you provide me with your date of birth for verification purposes?
Of course, I was born on June third, one nine eight zero.
Thank you for the information, Cheryl. Is there anything specific you would like to inquire about your policy today?
Yes, I would like to add a new vehicle to my policy.
I can assist you with that. Let's go ahead and get the details of the vehicle you wish to add.
Thank you for your time, Cheryl. If you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
